                        <p>
                            Kuwait may be small, but it has played a prominent role in the U.S. military’s operations in the Middle East for well over twenty years. As the terror group ISIS / ISIL and other similar organizations develop and spread in the area, Kuwait remains an important partner for the U.S. in the region.
                        </p>

